data.description: This is a must see!!! This is a rare find in a well sought after area. 4 bedrooms 2.5 baths with a 2 car garage. Open kitchen with granite countertops. Open concept that leads into the family room makes it perfect for entertaining. The master bedroom sits off by itself and has plenty of space in addition to the bathroom having a separate standup shower from the large tub. Every woman wants a large walk in closet like this one. The second bedroom downstairs can serve as a great office space with a row of book shelves. Upstairs bedroom has a custom closet system that is staying. All TVs' upstairs will remain as well The backyard has a pergola that is great for outdoor relaxing. Backyard is large enough for a pool. Laundry room has shelving that will remain as well.
